NK011(da)002:0: rong phur bla ma brgyud pa'i gsol 'debs bzhugs /
NK011(da)002:1: ston pa kun bzang rdo rje gzhon nu dang //
NK011(da)002:2: bram ze chen po mi yi thod pa can //
NK011(da)002:3: mkha' 'gro'i gtso mo las kyi dbang mo che //
NK011(da)002:4: pra b+ha hasti rnams la gsol ba 'debs //
NK011(da)002:5: u pa d+aa na o rgyan pad+ma 'byung //
NK011(da)002:6: rdo rje bdud 'joms dpal gyi dbang phyug dang //
NK011(da)002:7: dpal gyi me tog gtsug tor gzhon nu'i zhabs //
NK011(da)002:8: yon tan grags pa rnams la gsol ba 'debs //
NK011(da)002:9: gu na rat+na dpal gyi rin chen dang //
NK011(da)002:10: rin chen tshul khrims rong zom chos bzang zhabs //
NK011(da)002:11: gzi 'bar ston dar ston seng jo sras dang //
NK011(da)002:12: ra spe 'bum dpal rnams la gsol ba 'debs //
NK011(da)002:13: kun dga' me dpung chos bzhad gser 'od dang //
NK011(da)002:14: 'od zer 'bum dang 'bum rgod dar ma brtan //
NK011(da)002:15: sra brtan rdo rje bsod she sed+ge dpal //
NK011(da)002:16: dge 'dun rin chen rnams la gsol ba 'debs //
NK011(da)002:17: dge rgyal rdo rje seng+ge blo gros bzang //
NK011(da)002:18: pa ra hi ta badz+ra sh+ai la dang //
NK011(da)002:19: phrin las lhun grub 'gyur med rdo rje'i zhabs //
NK011(da)002:20: 'gyur med rgya mtsho rnams la gsol ba 'debs //
NK011(da)002:21: rin chen rnam rgyal pad+ma bstan 'dzin dang //
NK011(da)002:22: o rgyan bstan 'dzin phrin las rnam par rgyal //
NK011(da)002:23: dpal 'byor rgya mtsho rig 'dzin bzang po dang //
NK011(da)002:24: pad+ma mang+ga rnams la gsol ba 'debs //
NK011(da)002:25: gzhan phan mtha' yas pad+ma rdo rje dang //
NK011(da)002:26: bstan pa'i nyi ma 'jigs med kun dga' dpal //
NK011(da)002:27: mdo sngags bstan 'dzin rigs bdag 'khor lo'i mgon //
NK011(da)002:28: phan bde'i 'od zer zhabs la brgyud srol kun 'dus rtsa ba'i bla ma dang //
NK011(da)002:29: mtha' yas dngos grub mchog stsol yi dam lha //
NK011(da)002:30: bar chad kun sel dpa' bo mkha' 'gro'i tshogs //
NK011(da)002:31: chos skyong srung mar bcas la thugs rje'i bdag nyid mgon po mchog rnams kyis //
NK011(da)002:32: bdag rgyud smin cing grol bar mdzad pa dang //
NK011(da)002:33: zab mo'i lam gyi 'gal rkyen kun zhi zhing //
NK011(da)002:34: mthun rkyen yid bzhin 'grub par byin gyis rlobs //
NK011(da)002:35: lam bzang tshe 'dir sgrub la brtson pa'i mthus //
NK011(da)002:36: thun mong lam lnga thun min rig 'dzin bzhis //
NK011(da)002:37: bgrod nas he ru ka dpal mngon byas te //
NK011(da)002:38: rang gzhan don gnyis 'grub par byin gyis rlobs //
NK011(da)002:39: zhes rgyal sras gzhan phan mtha' yas kyis mdzad pa'i
NK011(da)002:40: brgyud 'debs la brgyud pa'i khyad par gyis gzhan phan
NK011(da)002:41: mtha' yas nas rigs bdag 'gyur med phan bde'i 'od
NK011(da)002:42: zer bar kha skong ba po ni 'jigs bral ye
